en_158342_0	President Maithripala Sirsena stated that he did not take the party leadership to place crowns on his family but to serve the general public.
en_158342_1	The president expressed these views addressing the SLFP National Youth Convention held at the Sugathadasa stadium today.
en_158342_2	President Sirisena also launched the official website of the SLFP Youth Front at the convention today.
